    <content_encoded><![CDATA[At long last we've worked out a method to offer <a href="/rt"><em>Rolling Thunder</em></a> subscriptions for a substantial discount without sacrificing quality or delivery speed—so, we are very excited to announce our new <a href="/rt/subscribe.html">two-year, four issue subscriptions</a>. Have four issues shipped to your door for just $22 (U.S.) and $25 (Global)— a respective savings of $10.64 and $44.60 versus ordering each issue separately. You can opt to start a subscription with the current issue or the next one; all the details, including an FAQ, are over on the <a href="/rt/subscribe.html">subscription page</a>. It has always been our goal to make <em>RT</em> available for as little money as possible while still sustaining itself, and we feel that these subscriptions are a solid step in both of those directions. In the meantime, we're working hard on RT#8, on schedule to ship at the beginning of September.]]></content_encoded>
